Package: xnatR
Type: Package
Title: Interface with XNAT Systems
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Bradley Buchsbaum [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Bradley Buchsbaum <brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com>
Authors@R: person("Bradley", "Buchsbaum",
    email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package for interacting with XNAT systems via the REST API.
    Provides functions to authenticate, list projects/subjects/experiments/scans,
    search, and download data from XNAT neuroimaging archives.
